---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE } from '@config/site';
---

<BaseLayout title={`${SITE.title} - Физиотерапия и рехабилитация`}>
  <!-- Hero Section - Sydney Theme Style -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background Image Slider (static for now) -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center bg-fixed" style="background-image: url('/images/backgrounds/burgas-bridge.jpg');"></div>
    <!-- Dark Overlay -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/70"></div>
    
    <!-- Hero Content -->
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-32 relative z-10 text-center">
      <div class="animate-fadeInRight">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 font-['Raleway'] leading-tight tracking-wide" style="text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);">
          "Вита" – Физиотерапевтичен Център
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-white/90 mb-10 font-light" style="text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);">
          Най-новите технологии в Бургас • 25 години опит в лечението на болката
        </p>
        <a
          href="#services"
          class="inline-block px-10 py-4 text-sm font-bold text-white bg-[#d65050] border-2 border-[#d65050] rounded uppercase tracking-wider font-['Raleway'] hover:bg-transparent transition-all duration-300"
        >
          Кликнете за да започнете
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Scroll indicator -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 z-10">
      <a href="#services" class="text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-colors">
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 animate-bounce" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services Section - Sydney Theme Style -->
  <section id="services" class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Section Title with underline -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold text-[#443f3f] uppercase relative inline-block pb-4 font-['Raleway']">
          Как можем да ви помогнем
          <span class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-12 h-0.5 bg-[#d65050]"></span>
        </h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-3">
        <!-- Service Card 1 - Experience -->
        <div class="text-center group">
          <div class="w-[70px] h-[70px] mx-auto mb-5 rounded-full bg-[#f7f7f7] flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-[#d65050] transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-[#d65050] group-hover:text-white transition-colors" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-[#443f3f] mb-4 font-['Raleway']">Опит</h3>
          <p class="text-[#767676] leading-relaxed">
            <strong>Добре дошли във физиотерапевтичен център "Вита" в град Бургас.</strong> От създаването на центъра през 2001 г. ние продължаваме да предлагаме най-високите стандарти за лечение и индивидуална грижа за пациентите от опитни специалисти по физикална и рехабилитационна медицина.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Service Card 2 - Complex Plan -->
        <div class="text-center group">
          <div class="w-[70px] h-[70px] mx-auto mb-5 rounded-full bg-[#f7f7f7] flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-[#d65050] transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-[#d65050] group-hover:text-white transition-colors" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-[#443f3f] mb-4 font-['Raleway']">Комплексен план</h3>
          <p class="text-[#767676] leading-relaxed">
            <strong>Чрез нашия комплексен план ние ще положим всички усилия, за да помогнем на тялото ви да се възстанови и да ви държи в движение.</strong>
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Service Card 3 - Treatment -->
        <div class="text-center group">
          <div class="w-[70px] h-[70px] mx-auto mb-5 rounded-full bg-[#f7f7f7] flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-[#d65050] transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-[#d65050] group-hover:text-white transition-colors" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M20 6h-4V4c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2h-4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v2H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V8c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zM10 4h4v2h-4V4zm6 11h-3v3h-2v-3H8v-2h3v-3h2v3h3v2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-[#443f3f] mb-4 font-['Raleway']">Лечение</h3>
          <p class="text-[#767676] leading-relaxed">
            <strong>Ние можем да ви уверим в най-доброто лечение, което е адаптирано за индивидуалните ви нужди.</strong> Ангажирани сме с дългосрочна грижа, за да сте сигурни, че достигате целите си за здраве, фитнес и естетика.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- News Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-[#f7f7f7]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold text-[#443f3f] uppercase relative inline-block pb-4 font-['Raleway']">
          Новости – Влог & Блог
          <span class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-12 h-0.5 bg-[#d65050]"></span>
        </h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
        <!-- News Card 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <a href="/telemedicine" class="block">
            <img src="/images/telemedicine.png" alt="Телемедицина" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" />
          </a>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#443f3f] mb-3 font-['Raleway']">
              <a href="/telemedicine" class="hover:text-[#d65050] transition-colors">Телемедицина</a>
            </h4>
            <p class="text-[#767676] text-sm line-clamp-3">
              Имате проблеми със ставите? Страдате от болка в гръбнака или различни автоимунни заболявания? Онлайн консултация – телемедицина...
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- News Card 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <a href="/news" class="block">
            <img src="/images/pregnancy-sports.jpg" alt="Бременност и спорт" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" />
          </a>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#443f3f] mb-3 font-['Raleway']">
              <a href="/news" class="hover:text-[#d65050] transition-colors">Бременност и спорт?</a>
            </h4>
            <p class="text-[#767676] text-sm line-clamp-3">
              "Защо не мога да тренирам по време на бременност?" Клиничните препоръки сочат, че жени без контраиндикации трябва да се ангажират с редовна физическа активност...
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- News Card 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <a href="/news" class="block">
            <img src="/images/nature-medicine.png" alt="Лекарства за Коронавирус" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" />
          </a>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#443f3f] mb-3 font-['Raleway']">
              <a href="/news" class="hover:text-[#d65050] transition-colors">Лекарства за Коронавирус: Хлороквин и Хидроксихлороквин</a>
            </h4>
            <p class="text-[#767676] text-sm line-clamp-3">
              Медикаменти използвани за COVID-19. Антималарици или нещо много повече?
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center mt-10">
        <a href="/news" class="inline-block px-10 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white bg-[#d65050] border-2 border-[#d65050] rounded uppercase tracking-wider font-['Raleway'] hover:bg-transparent hover:text-[#d65050] transition-all duration-300">
          Вижте още
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Diseases Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold text-[#443f3f] uppercase relative inline-block pb-4 font-['Raleway']">
          Заболявания
          <span class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-12 h-0.5 bg-[#d65050]"></span>
        </h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
        <!-- Disease Card 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <a href="/diseases" class="block">
            <img src="/images/diseases/osteoarthritis.png" alt="Остеоартроза" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" />
          </a>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#443f3f] mb-3 font-['Raleway']">
              <a href="/diseases" class="hover:text-[#d65050] transition-colors">Остеоартроза</a>
            </h4>
            <p class="text-[#767676] text-sm line-clamp-3">
              Остеоартрозата е хетерогенно разстройство, характеризиращо се с прогресивна загуба на хрущял...
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Disease Card 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <a href="/diseases" class="block">
            <img src="/images/diseases/degenerative-disk.png" alt="Дискова болест" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" />
          </a>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#443f3f] mb-3 font-['Raleway']">
              <a href="/diseases" class="hover:text-[#d65050] transition-colors">Дегенеративна дискова болест</a>
            </h4>
            <p class="text-[#767676] text-sm line-clamp-3">
              Дегенеративната дискова болест е състояние, което засяга междупрешленните дискове...
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Disease Card 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <a href="/diseases" class="block">
            <img src="/images/diseases/bells-palsy.jpg" alt="Парализа на Бел" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" />
          </a>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#443f3f] mb-3 font-['Raleway']">
              <a href="/diseases" class="hover:text-[#d65050] transition-colors">Парализа на Бел</a>
            </h4>
            <p class="text-[#767676] text-sm line-clamp-3">
              Парализата на Бел е внезапна слабост или парализа на лицевите мускули от едната страна на лицето...
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center mt-10">
        <a href="/diseases" class="inline-block px-10 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white bg-[#d65050] border-2 border-[#d65050] rounded uppercase tracking-wider font-['Raleway'] hover:bg-transparent hover:text-[#d65050] transition-all duration-300">
          Всички заболявания
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Partners Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-[#f7f7f7]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#443f3f] uppercase relative inline-block pb-4 font-['Raleway']">
          Партньори
          <span class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-12 h-0.5 bg-[#d65050]"></span>
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-8 md:gap-16">
        <img src="/images/partners/btl.png" alt="BTL" class="h-16 object-contain grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all opacity-70 hover:opacity-100" />
        <img src="/images/partners/chatanooga.png" alt="Chattanooga" class="h-16 object-contain grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all opacity-70 hover:opacity-100" />
        <img src="/images/partners/fisioline.png" alt="Fisioline" class="h-16 object-contain grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all opacity-70 hover:opacity-100" />
        <img src="/images/partners/guna.jpg" alt="Guna" class="h-16 object-contain grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all opacity-70 hover:opacity-100" />
        <img src="/images/partners/mdm.png" alt="MDM" class="h-16 object-contain grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all opacity-70 hover:opacity-100" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="relative py-24 bg-cover bg-center bg-fixed" style="background-image: url('/images/backgrounds/clinic.jpg');">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/70"></div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6 font-['Raleway']">
          Готови ли сте да се погрижите за здравето си?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-white/80 mb-10">
          Свържете се с нас днес и запазете своя час за консултация.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-block px-10 py-4 text-sm font-bold text-white bg-[#d65050] border-2 border-[#d65050] rounded uppercase tracking-wider font-['Raleway'] hover:bg-transparent transition-all duration-300"
          >
            Свържете се с нас
          </a>
          <a
            href="/procedures"
            class="inline-block px-10 py-4 text-sm font-bold text-white border-2 border-white/50 rounded uppercase tracking-wider font-['Raleway'] hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-300"
          >
            Вижте процедурите
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
